metadata.name: Exposed to Liberation
metadata.description:
On her ’Last Struggle’ in the dark and dense silence she hears : strive or surrender... THE ONLY WAY OUT IS IN

Q u i e t ,
Trapped in silence.
She sense the pull out the Self, so subtle.
She feels love, she finds love, she is love.

She is breaking in - turning the trapped into the flow.
She merges with the Self and become one with the Divine.
For the sake of love, love of the Divine Self.
